parameters:
\nw[Taro]Phew... As expected, things are different on the
sea...

\nw[Taro]I wonder if the others are okay... I should check
on Shia's condition.

\nw[Shia]There's no one around. It's because I don't want
anyone to hear my voice.

\nw[Taro](She's whispering in my ear in a low voice, it's a
little dangerous...)

\nw[Taro]It seems like it depends on the monsters and the
wind, but it's about half a day? They said it's
close, but it seems like there's still a
considerable distance.

\nw[Shia]Half a day, understood. Are there any problems
with the monsters?
\nw[Taro]Ah, it seems like we can defeat them.

\nw[Taro](Damn, I've been dragged into the sea...! I have
to save Shia and get back!)

\nw[Taro](No, there's no time to think... We have to
quickly defeat the monster that captured Shia!)
\nw[Kuno]The boat is rocking, it feels strange.

\nw[Nonna]It would be good if you can safely make it to the
island.

\nw[Taro]H-Hey, if you're feeling sick, you can puke in the
sea, okay?

\nw[Fross]I specialize in complex treatments and I'm not
good at first aid. I can't treat things like
seasickness.

\nw[Thorz]It's not disgusting... It's not disgusting... It's
not disgusting... I'm fine... I'm fine... I'm
fine... I'm not drunk... I'm not drunk...

\nw[Dalton]Even at my age, I have very little experience with
naval battles. This rocking is quite troublesome.

\nw[Huma]Oops, my sense of balance is bad. It seems like
doing something erotic wouldn't be fun.

\nw[Rodrigo]I've been an adventurer for quite a long time, but
there's hardly any experience on the sea. It's an
environment with no escape, and if there are women
here, I can have my way with them as much as I
want...!

\nw[Crew member]You've got a nice body, don't you? How about
having some fun with me?
